To do this automatically as part of your build, configure the [maven-source-plugin](https://maven.apache.org/plugins/maven-source-plugin/jar-mojo.html) to bind to the appropriate phase of your build:

    &lt;plugin&gt;
		&lt;groupId&gt;org.apache.maven.plugins&lt;/groupId&gt;
		&lt;artifactId&gt;maven-source-plugin&lt;/artifactId&gt;
		&lt;executions&gt;
			&lt;execution&gt;
