					&lt;goal&gt;jar&lt;/goal&gt;
				&lt;/goals&gt;
			&lt;/execution&gt;
		&lt;/executions&gt;
	&lt;/plugin&gt;

This will create an additional jar file with the `source` classifier, ie: `&lt;your-artifact-name&gt;-source.jar`

